      <h2><i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"></i>About This App</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to the LEGO Set Finder — your ultimate source for discovering and exploring LEGO sets from 1964 to 2021. This app provides a variety of search filters to help you locate your favorite sets and organize them into wishlists or owned collections.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're a passionate LEGO collector or enjoy building casually, this app lets you keep track of the sets you own and the ones you want. Sign up to enable your personal wishlist and owned-set lists.
      </p>
      <p>
        The search filters streamline the process of finding specific sets — by theme, year, name, price range, or set number. Start exploring the world of LEGO sets today!
      </p>

      <h2><i class="bi bi-gear-fill me-2"></i>Features</h2>
      <p>
        Search by name, theme, year, set number, or price range. Use the advanced multi-filter to combine up to three criteria at once. Add sets to your wishlist or mark them as owned. Manage a personal ideas list for sets you're considering.
      </p>

